gisp audit logs
===============

Copyright (C) 2026 Uladzislau Bolbas <cmrtumilovic@gmail.com>

The .log files in this directory (adversarial.log, layout.log) are captured
transcripts produced by the audit scripts (adversarial.sh and the constants
helper).  As mechanically generated output they do not carry their own
copyright and license notices, so this README records them here, as
recommended by the GNU/Savannah documentation on copyright notices
(http://www.gnu.org/prep/maintain/html_node/Copyright-Notices.html).

Copying and distribution of these files, with or without modification, are
permitted in any medium without royalty provided the copyright notice and
this notice are preserved.  They are offered as-is, without any warranty.

The audit tooling itself (adversarial.sh, byteflip.c, constants.c) and the
report (report.md) carry their own notices and state their licenses.
